Ogige Tinubu (nke bụbu ebe nwepu onwe), bụ ihe ngosi oghere dị na Broad Street, Lagos Island, Lagos State, Nigeria agụlu ya aha site ịtụ mgbere ohu bụ onye Yoruba ohu na-ere ahịa, onye ahịa, na aristocrat Madam Efunroye Tinubu. A na-akpọbu ya Ita Tinubu tupu ndị isi nke First Nigerian Republic akpọ ya Independence Square mgbe nnwere onwe Naịjirịa gasịrị na Tinubu ogige.
Ogige ahụ nwere ígwè na-egbochi ya na isi iyi abụọ na-asọ asọ, okooko osisi na osisi ndị na-ekpo ọkụ na ya
O nwekwara ihe oyiyi nke Madam Tinubu na cenotaph.
